graph TB
    subgraph "CodeFlare Operator"
        Manager[CodeFlare Operator Manager]
        MCAD[MCAD Controller<br/>Queue-based Workload Scheduling]
        InstaScale[InstaScale Controller<br/>Optional, OpenShift Only]
        MetricsServer[Metrics Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        HealthProbe[Health Probe Server<br/>8081/TCP HTTP]

        Manager -->|embeds| MCAD
        Manager -->|embeds| InstaScale
        Manager -->|exposes| MetricsServer
        Manager -->|exposes| HealthProbe
    end

    User[User/Client] -->|creates| AppWrapperCR[AppWrapper CR<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta1]
    User -->|creates| SchedulingSpecCR[SchedulingSpec CR<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta1]
    User -->|creates| QuotaSubtreeCR[QuotaSubtree CR<br/>quota.codeflare.dev/v1alpha1]

    AppWrapperCR -->|watched by| MCAD
    SchedulingSpecCR -->|watched by| MCAD
    QuotaSubtreeCR -->|watched by| Manager

    MCAD -->|creates| Pods[Pods/Deployments/Jobs]
    MCAD -->|creates| RayCluster[RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io]
    MCAD -->|creates| Services[Services/ConfigMaps]

    InstaScale -->|watches| AppWrapperCR
    InstaScale -->|monitors| Nodes[Cluster Nodes]
    InstaScale -->|creates/deletes| MachineSet[MachineSet CR<br/>machine.openshift.io]

    RayCluster -->|watched by| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]
    KubeRay -->|creates| RayPods[Ray Head/Worker Pods]

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes| MetricsServer
    Kubelet[Kubelet] -->|probes| HealthProbe

    MachineSet -->|provisions| CloudAPI[Cloud Provider API<br/>AWS/GCP/Azure]

    style Manager fill:#4a90e2
    style MCAD fill:#4a90e2
    style InstaScale fill:#4a90e2
    style MetricsServer fill:#4a90e2
    style HealthProbe fill:#4a90e2
    style AppWrapperCR fill:#f5a623
    style SchedulingSpecCR fill:#f5a623
    style QuotaSubtreeCR fill:#f5a623
    style RayCluster fill:#f5a623
    style MachineSet fill:#f5a623
    style KubeRay fill:#7ed321
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321
    style CloudAPI fill:#e8e8e8
